{
  "stem": "9102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was just left off where I came to the others with-- in Heerlen with Miss Johanna Hookstat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She is the one who took me into her house, being a single lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was told that if I were asked, I was one of the nephews from the city of Rotterdam that was bombed out during-- at the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of those kids were, you know, put down, not hidden as such, all-- you know, moved all over the country in order to, you know, to basically survive the war, since all the homes were all bombed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like I mentioned before, this lady lived on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here sister and-- and brother-in-law lived downstairs with three kids-- two boys and a girl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The boys were basically-- the oldest boy was more or less my age-- a few years younger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I just-- I had a normal life with them while, of course, in the beginning, I was very sad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, there was-- And I was told, oh, it's just for a few, you know, few weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The war, you know, the war will be over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And be-- and you can go back home to your parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I kind of like [? imagined ?] the underground was quite often in and out of the house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They told me to write a letter, which-- [? what ?] they would take to my parents, which I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wrote them a letter that I was, you know, wanted to come home and all this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, all-- all basically this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, I don't know, a week later or so, I got a letter back from the [INAUDIBLE] underground, what wasn't supposed to be from my parents.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
